<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog Page Example</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #333;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .navbar a {
            float: left;
            display: block;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .navbar a:hover {
            background-color: #ddd;
            color: black;
        }

        .blog-post {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .blog-post img {
            width: 100%;
            max-height: 400px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .blog-post-content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .blog-post-content h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .blog-post-content .author {
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .blog-post-content .message {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .blog-post-content .email {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555555;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="blog">Blog</a>
        <a href="create-blog">Create Blog</a>
        <a href="about">About</a>
        <a href="contact_list">Contact-List</a>

    </div>

    <div class="blog-post">
        <img src="blog-post-image.jpg" alt="Blog Post Image">
        <div class="blog-post-content">
            <h2>How to Create a Blog Page with HTML and CSS</h2>
            <p class="author">By John Doe</p>
            <p class="message">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla eget lectus quam. Donec id
                ipsum at ipsum rhoncus vehicula. Nullam suscipit mollis orci, in viverra lectus feugiat at. Donec
                pretium, neque nec consequat.</p>
            <p class="email">Contact the author: john.doe@example.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>